subsections.content:
The declared unit is 1 m2. The sizes of the stones can vary from:
• Length 29 cm;
• Hight between 9 cm – 19 cm;
• Width 22 cm.

In this EPD, the Carbstone Kimblok are reported with the sizes: 29/09/22, 29/14/22, 29/19/22. The representative Carbstone has the sizes 29/09/22.

The amount of glue and the amount of carbstone (in mass) differ when other sizes are used. The carbstone has the most influence on environmental impact categories Climate change – total, Resource use minerals and metals, and Respiratory inorganics.
